{"tid":2163521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠康指須研「保就業」計劃額外要求　重申已作多項回饋","createTime":"2020-08-18T17:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T17:09:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5989af78e6ad7e47568710bdcbb951835a169ab","tid":2163521,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"惠康超級市場回覆查詢時表示，正仔細研究計劃詳情及要求，並樂意向政府了解更多細節。<br />\n<br />\n惠康表示，在數月前起，已進行多項回饋社會行動，包括捐出逾一萬份社區愛心包給港澳的獨居長者、殘疾人士等，同時曾為有需要社群安排優先購物服務。<br />\n<br />\n另外，惠康上周亦宣布將捐贈10萬張餐券予社會有需要人士，逾15個慈善團體預計可於下月初獲得首批餐券，並派發予有需要人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544495-20200819.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544495-20200819.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=a12260b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544495-20200819.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9e1ad8f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544495-20200819.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7be71abd490a11d027e463c8ddd2481a98d06e2a","tid":2163521,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}